  "description": "Guru Bin signature #2. Double-peak arc over 12 seconds \u2014 the overture and the climax. First peak brings partial alignment to 60% (the overture), a dip to 30% (intermission), second peak drives to 95% (the climax). Formant morphs A-to-O as the arc rises. Theatrical. The curtain does not simply rise \u2014 it rises twice.",
